snippet.title: Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six: Rogue Spear Commercial from 1999
snippet.description: Commercial for Tom Clancy's Rogue Spear video game for PC.  Recorded on VHS during an episode of WWF Raw is War on USA on September 27th, 1999.
